<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <title>硬件的屏幕分辨率</title>
    <style>
        .wrap{
            width: 1200px;
            height: 180px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            margin-top: 100px;
            background-color:antiquewhite;
            text-align: center;
            padding-top: 30px;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body style="margin: 0; padding: 0; border: 0">
<div class="wrap">
    <h3>1、screen.width硬件的分辨率</h3>
    <script>
        document.write(screen.width+"<br>");
        document.write(screen.height+"<br>");
    </script>
</div>


<div class="wrap">
    <h3>2、screen.avalblewidth,硬件的分辨率但不操作系统含状态栏的尺寸</h3>
    <script>
        document.write(screen.availWidth+"<br>");
        document.write(screen.availHeight+"<br>");
    </script>
</div>
<div class="wrap">
    <h3>3、client.width,浏览器的可视区域大小，不含浏览器的标题栏目、搜索框、工具栏，状态栏，以及操作系统的状态栏，但包含右侧和底部的</h3>
    <script>
        var W=window.innerWidth||document.documentElement.clientWidth||document.body.clientWidth;
        var H=window.innerHeight||document.documentElement.clientWidth||document.body.clientHeight;
        document.write("浏览器当前可视的宽度时："+W+"<br>");
        document.write("浏览器当前可视的高度是："+H+"<br>");
    </script>
</div>
<div class="wrap">
    <h3>4、scrollWidth 获取网页内容的实际宽高,啥都不含，只含内容,当小于client.width时，返回client值</h3>
    <script>
        var W=document.documentElement.scrollWidth||document.body.scrollWidth;
        var H=document.documentElement.scrollHeight||document.body.scrollHeight;
        document.write(W+"<br>");
        document.write(H+"<br>");
    </script>
</div>
<div class="wrap">
    <h3>5、offsetWidth 获取网页内容高度和宽度。宽度随窗口的缩放而改变，当小于client.width时，返回client值
       </h3>
    <script>
        var W=document.documentElement.offsetWidth||document.body.offsetWidth;
        var H=document.documentElement.offsetHeight||document.body.offsetHeight;
        document.write(W+"<br>");
        document.write(H+"<br>");
    </script>
</div>
</body>
</html>